Test Function

Source: R/rNFFT.R
test_nfft.Rd

Test Function

test_nfft(m, n)

test_solve(m, n, iterations)

nfft_test_2d()

Arguments

m

integer, number of nodes
n

integer, number of frequences (even, less than m).
iterations

Number of iterations (for solver)

Value

TRUE

Details

Generates Test Output specified in NFFT documentation and source code. Compare the output to the results of the examples.

Functions

  • test_solve: Test solver: displays the 1D solver.

  • nfft_test_2d: 2D test: displays the 2D test (no input)

Examples

set.seed(20190722)
